videos.headline: Lawrence extends Clemson's lead with 2nd TD pass
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence finds Tee Higgins for a 3-yard touchdown pass, giving Clemson a 14-0 lead over Florida State.

videos.headline: Clemson's D picks off Francois
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois gets hit as he throws and Clemson linebacker Tre Lamar returns an interception 43 yards into FSU territory.

videos.headline: Clemson 300-pound DL rushes for TD
videos.description: Clemson defensive lineman Christian Wilkins plunges in for a touchdown from the 1-yard line to put the Tigers up 21-0 over Florida State.

videos.headline: FSU DB ejected for hit on Lawrence
videos.description: Florida State defensive back Hamsah Nasirildeen lays a hit on Clemson's Trevor Lawrence and is ejected for targeting in the 2nd quarter.

videos.headline: Lawrence's 3rd TD pass goes 58 yards to Rodgers
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence finds Amari Rodgers on a short slant and Rodgers takes it 58 yards for a Clemson touchdown early in the 2nd half.

videos.headline: Lawrence hits Rodgers for 2nd TD pass over 50 yards
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence connects with Amari Rodgers on a touchdown pass for the second time vs. Florida State, this time from 68 yards out.

videos.headline: Clemson backup Brice throws short TD
videos.description: Clemson backup quarterback Chase Brice scrambles out of the pocket and throws a 5-yard strike to T.J. Chase for another Clemson touchdown.

videos.headline: Clemson RB Choice runs for 15-yard TD
videos.description: Clemson running back Adam Choice runs through the Florida State defense and scores a 15-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson RB Choice runs for 15-yard TD) 2018/10/27

videos.headline: FSU finally scores TD from 73 yards out
videos.description: Florida State's first touchdown vs. Clemson comes late in the 4th quarter on a 73-yard touchdown pass from James Blackman to Keyshawn Helton.
